snippet.title: Manitas Kitchen - Official Gameplay Video | Wholesome Direct 2023
snippet.description: Get cooking in this short gameplay video for Manitas Kitchen, an upcoming a casual cooking game with a dressing of arcade and mini-games, where you'll meet Trexito, a T-Rex with short arms that has one dream: to become the best pizza maker.
